{"tid":1985032,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲擬趁原油供給過剩 在美設置戰略儲備","createTime":"2020-04-23T01:17:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T15:25:18.000Z","uid":141151,"like":223,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"eefa2488bbd55ddb1cfb57fa26e43b7ad82bd141","tid":1985032,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T01:17:34.000Z","msg":"澳洲擬趁原油供給過剩 在美設置戰略儲備<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4510951\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F4510951&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6g%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=c10fa808\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4510951</a><br />\n<br />\n澳洲今天表示，將利用國際油價創新低之際，著手建立戰略儲備，地點將在美國。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲能源部長泰勒（Angus Taylor ）表示，澳洲將斥資9400萬澳元（約新台幣18億2548萬元），開始在美國建立石油儲備。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲長期以來一直是緊急石油儲備最低的已開發國家國家之一，一旦荷莫茲海峽等地緣政治重要性高的地區情勢緊張，澳洲便容易暴露在風險中。<br />\n<br />\n泰勒說：「這是開始建立原油儲備的好機會，因為我們見到油價來到歷史性低點。」"},{"pid":"c0619a88b154d7392a7062f97a9ea2f33c034e81","tid":1985032,"uid":333199,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T01:18:37.000Z","msg":"醒WOR"},{"pid":"c16b7246d618d4bc889ef4d457636640518414fc","tid":1985032,"uid":15954,"like":21,"dislike":8,"score":13,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T01:19:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔自己國家到起"},{"pid":"c18f55dd8a792e963e4ef02ba198000dc3fb2fb7","tid":1985032,"uid":110079,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T01:19:30.000Z","msg":"今次終於唔係同支共合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5853f776594e0ff24f9e6a737be314a8b146698e","tid":1985032,"uid":345989,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T01:20:57.000Z","msg":"起係美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed1b6322beb5048b033ca3779b80321fca39b42c","tid":1985032,"uid":61494,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"c16b7246d618d4b